				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Tradeskills... which ones for bards?<a name="50117"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 5 04 3:53 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>If you're doing brewing, please don't do Mino Hero's brew from skill 0.
<br />

<br />
Pick up a giant cyclops skull from South Karana and you can do Skull Ale. The recipie is much easier and will get you to 151. (I realize that with the new interface 'easier' only means less trips to the vendor, but it does make a difference.)
<br />

<br />
Quick Note: the skull is GIANT sized, so you need to carry a spit, etc if you don't have a free top slot. I kept mine in my spit next to my OT hammer when skilling.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, when you are done, you can always pass the skull along to a new brewer.
<br />

<br />
Happy Tradeskilling,
<br />
Aelf</span></td>
