				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Jarroll is not online. Last active: 9/9/2004 12:15:30 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Jarroll">Jarroll</a><br><a class="SmallText" href="http://www.xegonybard.com" target="_new">www.xegonybard.com</a></td>
